    "description": "东方秘剑录，是一款横板卷轴动作游戏。游戏有独特的战斗系统，玩家在关卡中做出不同的决定，会导致关底触发不同的剧情，正面挑战更强的BOSS或者用别的方式“逃课”都取决于玩家。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >★关于故事★</h2>一道光芒从天而降，周围突然升起谜之建筑，神秘卷轴出现在幻想乡，作为一号闲人的琪露诺决定去看个究竟！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >★在关卡中会遇到各种有趣的事情★</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791610/extras/b54de995315d982bb5d4f302ff3c7be6.poster.avif?t=1664612936\" width=626 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791610/extras/b54de995315d982bb5d4f302ff3c7be6.webm?t=1664612936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791610/extras/b54de995315d982bb5d4f302ff3c7be6.mp4?t=1664612936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >★玩家可以在关卡中解锁新的技能★</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791610/extras/5c81c0ee9c4f4f563e3e5185ebb3b51b.poster.avif?t=1664612936\" width=622 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791610/extras/5c81c0ee9c4f4f563e3e5185ebb3b51b.webm?t=1664612936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791610/extras/5c81c0ee9c4f4f563e3e5185ebb3b51b.mp4?t=1664612936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791610/extras/715afd66d1a55b857f84b810fa2546d7.poster.avif?t=1664612936\" width=622 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791610/extras/715afd66d1a55b857f84b810fa2546d7.webm?t=1664612936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamsta